@startuml 2C_Manage_Platform_Links
title 2-C · Manage Social & External Links (UC-T06, UC-T18, UC-F10, UC-F11)

start
|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
:Open Social Links / External Sites manager;
if (Admin action?) then (Add Link)
  :Enter URL, label, platform type and sort order;
  |System|
  :Validate URL format and tenant scope;
  :Fetch optional metadata\n(preview title and thumbnail);
  if (Fetch successful?) then (No)
    |Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
    :Confirm saving without preview;
  else (Yes)
    |Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
    :Show preview title and thumbnail;
  endif
  |System|
  :Save link as active;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Reorder)
  :Drag and drop link order;
  |System|
  :Update sort_order for tenant links;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Hide / Show)
  :Toggle selected link visibility;
  |System|
  :Update is_active flag;
else (Delete)
  :Delete selected link;
  |System|
  :Remove or soft-delete link record;
endif

|System|
:Invalidate fansite cache;

|Anonymous Visitor / Registered Fan|
:View external link list on idol profile;
:Click external link;

|System|
:Record click analytics if enabled;
:Redirect to external platform;
stop
@enduml
